1
00:00:36,040 --> 00:00:39,930
For one still so young,
your calligraphy is highly conformist.

2
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:44,800
I don't know if it's better
described as copybook-style,

3
00:00:44,800 --> 00:00:47,470
or made simply to win calligraphy awards.

4
00:00:48,060 --> 00:00:52,120
Did you even attempt to scale
the wall of mediocrity?

5
00:00:52,820 --> 00:00:59,200
Eika Prize Award Reception

6
00:00:53,360 --> 00:00:55,360
With all due respect, Director...

7
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:58,910
Managing the hall for many years
has given me a discerning eye.

8
00:00:59,890 --> 00:01:01,860
And your calligraphy is just plain dull.

9
00:01:03,710 --> 00:01:06,380
Say, I took these photos earlier...

10
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,430
Hey! Handa!

11
00:01:09,610 --> 00:01:12,020
What's wrong with my calligraphy?!

12
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,880
What are you doing, you idiot?!

13
00:01:23,880 --> 00:01:26,670
Let me go! He can't insult me like that!

14
00:01:26,670 --> 00:01:29,580
He doesn't even know how hard I've worked!

15
00:01:29,580 --> 00:01:30,290
Ow!

16
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:45,910
1 New Message

17
00:01:45,910 --> 00:01:47,410
From Kawafuji
Sub [None]
How's the island?

18
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,420
Not much to it...

19
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,710
Airport
Gotou Bus

20
00:01:54,710 --> 00:01:56,720
Runs 6/14-7/31

21
